## External Tools (not bundled)

### Coli (@marswave/coli)

VoiceX can optionally invoke the `coli` CLI for local offline speech
recognition. Coli is a separate NPM package and is NOT included in
this repository. Users who wish to use local ASR must install it
independently. See https://www.npmjs.com/package/@marswave/coli for
its license terms.


## Rust & JavaScript Dependencies

All other dependencies are fetched via Cargo (Rust) and pnpm (JavaScript)
at build time. Their licenses can be inspected via:

- Rust: `cargo license` (install with `cargo install cargo-license`)
- JavaScript: `pnpm licenses list`
